{"id": 1607, "genre": 1000, "title": "喜欢的影视剧改编为中国版，你最大的担忧是什么？", "description": "可能是笑场……（题图来自：Death of the Firstborn Egyptians）", "record_count": 35393, "comment_count": 124, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201704020814362o5nUBxjRIJDs1iE.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-04-06T17:00:17Z", "questions": [{"id": 2128, "title": "喜欢的影视剧改编为中国版，你最大的担忧是什么？", "content": "喜欢的影视剧改编为中国版，你最大的担忧是什么？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 186546, "content": "演技成谜的当红小鲜肉来演经典角色", "image": "img/option/option/20170402082132jVSF80YJvKsCXodO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 186547, "content": "不顾剧情需要强行增减情节，改编后逻辑混乱", "image": "img/option/option/20170402081943hOqFLwj3MkT1PEAV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 186549, "content": "为了适应中国特色/审查，毁剧本", "image": "img/option/option/20170402082047XtoPLidZq7kfuIVN.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 186550, "content": "每隔十分钟就强行植入矿泉水、牛奶、汽车logo", "image": "img/option/option/20170402082118wSr3DhTlgHbq0GsZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 186551, "content": "无论本来是什么类型的电影，最后都能拍成爱情片", "image": "img/option/option/20170402082201RXTozUcZn4yrY27B.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 186552, "content": "不管了，先加个五毛特效", "image": "img/option/option/20170402082226bsPQSRpDeauYxwEt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 186553, "content": "别国场景特有的风味，到国产版总成了城乡结合部", "image": "img/option/option/20170402082254JjgwXKx4DaZdoNG6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 186554, "content": "直译经典台词，听起来超尴尬", "image": "img/option/option/20170402082338u4UAZgwKBexnNPrM.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}